load ../owned-harness-envelope.maude

--- Coverage (budget): with a budget token, a model step occurs.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-OWNED-HARNESS-ENVELOPE :
  running budgetToken
  =>* C:Cfg modelStepped .

--- Coverage (lease): while the workspace lease is held, a tool runs.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-OWNED-HARNESS-ENVELOPE :
  running workspaceLease
  =>* C:Cfg toolRan .

--- Bite (budget): with no budget token, no model step is ever reachable. The
--- RESIDUAL soup var means any modelStepped in any reachable state is a solution,
--- so No solution proves the budget bounds the loop.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-OWNED-HARNESS-ENVELOPE :
  running
  =>* modelStepped RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite (lease): with no held lease, no tool is ever reachable.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-OWNED-HARNESS-ENVELOPE :
  running
  =>* toolRan RESIDUAL:Cfg .

--- Bite (release bounds tool use): once the lease is released, no further tool
--- execution is reachable.
search [1] in WHIPPLESCRIPT-OWNED-HARNESS-ENVELOPE :
  running leaseReleased
  =>* toolRan RESIDUAL:Cfg .
